---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy of Campeonato Pasos Libres: what data we collect, how we use it and what rights you have."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="section legal">
    <div class="container legal-inner">
      <h1 class="script-title">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p>
        At Campeonato Pasos Libres (www.campeonatopasoslibres.com), we are committed to protecting the
        privacy of our participants and users. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, how
        long we keep it and what rights you have over it.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Person in Charge of the Treatment</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Responsible: Evelyn Viana Lovera</li>
        <li>Tax Identification Number: X-2449338-E</li>
        <li>Address: Arc de Sant Sever, 7, 1º, 08026, Barcelona</li>
        <li>E-mail: <a href="mailto:info@lanegrasalsa.com">info@lanegrasalsa.com</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you register or interact with us, we may collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Registration data: name, surname, email, telephone, nationality, category of participation.</li>
        <li>Audiovisual material: photos and videos captured during the event.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
      <p>We use your data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Manage your registration and participation.</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about the event.</li>
        <li>Publish results on the web and social networks.</li>
        <li>Disseminate and promote the championship through audiovisual content.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not share your data with third parties without your consent, unless legally required to do so.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Legal Basis</h2>
      <p>The treatment is based on:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Execution of a contract (participation in the event).</li>
        <li>Compliance with legal obligations (e.g., tax).</li>
        <li>Legitimate interest (promotion of the event).</li>
        <li>Consent (for certain publications and communications).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Conservation Period</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Registration data: up to 12 months after the event, unless otherwise required by law.</li>
        <li>
          Audiovisual material: at least 5 years for promotional purposes. Some of the content may be kept
          indefinitely on the web/social networks.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You can request the removal of audiovisual content by writing to
        <a href="mailto:info@lanegrasalsa.com">info@lanegrasalsa.com</a>, and your request will be evaluated
        according to the legitimate interest of the event and the rights of third parties.
      </p>

      <h2>6. User Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access to your personal data.</li>
        <li>Correct incorrect or incomplete data.</li>
        <li>Request the deletion of your data.</li>
        <li>Oppose treatment.</li>
        <li>Limit treatment.</li>
        <li>Request the portability of your data.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise them, please send an email to
        <a href="mailto:info@lanegrasalsa.com">info@lanegrasalsa.com</a> with the subject “Data Protection”.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can also file a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD) if you consider that
        your rights have not been respected.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data against
        unauthorized access, loss or alteration.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Changes in Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This policy may be updated to reflect changes in the law or improvements to our services. We
        encourage you to review it periodically.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or wish to exercise your rights, please contact us:
        <a href="mailto:info@lanegrasalsa.com">info@lanegrasalsa.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal {
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .legal-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px);
    margin: 40px 0 14px;
  }
  .legal p {
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }
  .legal ul {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    padding-left: 22px;
  }
  .legal li {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .legal a {
    color: var(--gold-dark);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
